name: Bubbo
description: Bubo is an all-in-one crypto tracker built on SUI, designed to help you explore and trade smarter. Track token performance in real time with the Bubbles Map, and spot hot trends across the ecosystem using the Heatmap. When it’s time to trade, Bubo Swap offers fast, secure swaps with optimized liquidity from top DEXs. Whether you’re a beginner or pro, Bubo makes crypto easy to navigate — simple, powerful, and made for everyone on SUI.
